            <thetext>Hello,

If a window has a padding then the window will look incorrect. Namely, the window&#39;s title bar will be padded also.
I suppose the padding should be applied to window&#39;s canvas not to the window itself.

Code snippet:

var wnd = new qx.ui.window.Window(&quot;Test&quot;);
wnd.set({
    padding : 5,
    left : 10,
    top : 10,
    width : 400,
    height : 300
});
wnd.addToDocument();
wnd.show();


Best regards,
Dioc</thetext>
